14:
That was one heck of a fall... 
Maybe someone'll find us here.
22:
Get away from here, Stella. 
I'll handle this!
26:
Not bad, kid. 
I’ll give you a gold star for that one.
40:
Way to stand your ground, kid. 
I'll treat you to a round back on the 
surface.
46:
The tremors are even more erratic 
this year. 
Let the rookies know.
49:
Understood. 
You kids sure were lucky Leon was there 
to save you!
52:
Yeah... So he's a big deal around here, 
huh?
57: He certainly gave off that aura.
61:
That's right! No adventurer compares to 
Leon! 
Fiends and monsters tremble at the 
sound of his name!
63:
He’s a legend who ventured into the 
depths of the Kaleidoscope and lived to 
tell the tale!
65:
And not only that—he's been all across 
the frontier, traversing countless 
unexplored territories and made it back 
unscathed—a man among men!
67:
Come on, tell us another tale of your 
journey, Leon!
70:
Heh... Look at you lot, all gathered 
around for storytime. 
You sure you kiddies are ready for the 
Kaleidoscope?
73:
You'll get your stories... 
But first, we feast! Here's to surviving 
another day!
77:
...And that's what happened at the 
Spawning Caverns. It shows that even 
the weakest beings can be a menace 
with numbers.
81:
Whoa... I bet you slashed 'em up just 
like when you came to our rescue!
84:
Trust me, it wasn't as cool as you're 
probably imagining it—
I was covered from head to toe in slime!
87:
But it was a mighty fun adventure, 
that's for sure.
92:
Why did you choose to become an 
adventurer?
98:
They say the grass is greener on the 
other side... 
but you never know unless you see for 
yourself, right?
100:
And that's not all— 
whether it's the shops down the road 
or scaling a mountain, 
I'm always driven by curiosity.
102:
I'm just another kid who had big 
dreams of exploring the Kaleidoscope, 
nothing more.
105:
I mean... 
There's nothin' like the thrill of 
adventure, am I right?
108:
All right, that's all you're gettin' out 
of me tonight! 
Time for all of youse to prepare for 
your next adventure!
113: Stella. You thinking what I'm thinking?
117:
I believe so. 
Let's see what Leon has to say.
122:
Huh... I was expecting this hideout to be 
a little more, well, incognito.
126:
Welcome to Starview Village. 
I am its Keeper, Stella.
131:
It's the least we could do for you after 
you saved us back there.
135:
Hey now... 
Is it all right for me to take all of this? 
You shouldn't have, really.
140:
Increased tremors, a mysterious town, 
and now these kids... Huh.
143:
Say, rookie—er, Alk, was it? 
I'd like to propose a deal between two 
adventurers.
145:
Let me stay here a while. 
In exchange, I'll teach you the ins and 
outs of being an adventurer. 
Sound good to you?
152:
Good? That sounds GREAT! 
We'd love to have you, Leon!
